title: Maximo Training and Certification Course Online
description: Mindmajix’s Maximo training will strengthen your skills and proficiency in IBM Maximo Asset Management. You will master the fundamental concepts and key features of asset management and its functionality through hands-on training sessions. You will also work on two real-time projects in our training which are in line with the IBM Maximo certification exam.
